{"tid":1865034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"50萬個口罩。快快入來。","createTime":"2020-02-06T03:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T03:22:19.000Z","uid":337498,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"310bc42c7ae15d7a6c9618620cabc1b3fb401f21","tid":1865034,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:08:24.000Z","msg":"轉載自某fb。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我有50萬個獨立包裝的口罩。<br />\n全德國製造。採用ATA技術，能99.47%隔擋病毒。賣5元一個。<br />\n圖片自行Google。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以在下面留言要幾多個。為了避免交收會令各位損失一個口罩。本人將使用順風快遞交貨。各位需提供明確的個人資料方便確認，並付清貨款，轉帳到中銀帳戶：8888 8888 8888 8888。<br />\n<br />\n記得like和分享。未有like和分享的將不會受理。<br />\n<br />\n備註：現今大多無良小公司為了刷知名度，用假post話有口罩呃人比like和分享。更有公司通過這種手段收集個人資料。我明白大家對這些問題的擔憂，雖然我沒有辦法證明自己不是這樣的人，但為了一點希望，為了一個口罩，都要咁做，都要落入佢地的陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n來啦！比個like來啦！呢個世界話唔埋，或者系真的。不個希望自己。"},{"pid":"978b1e1671750f3936271fe068cb334d18112f28","tid":1865034,"uid":22692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:10:05.000Z","msg":"拉 哂我時間"},{"pid":"c9d887dbacf8fa36ea789ad39344dce36d912801","tid":1865034,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"明顯騙徒<br />\n<br />\n仲貼戶口號碼"},{"pid":"ed30f9ee4ed2d818a15c6fe8b9f9e8c2daadd821","tid":1865034,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"$250 50個？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52856fd6edcb25e457551789f593f61135e13526","tid":1865034,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"8888888888888<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a82f7